text: Browserslist is the shared browser compatibility config for popular JavaScript tools like Autoprefixer, Babel, ESLint, Next.js, PostCSS, and Webpack. Now it's got a new website at https://browsersl.ist where you can test audience coverage and behold some hedgehogs.
